规定，坚定理想信念，牢记党的宗旨，绝不能在宗教中寻找自己的价值和信念。”", "timestamp": 1597410654, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 249798, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 47576, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得这里只是引用土话显得亲切，并且看语境可以将神明理解成“正义”", "timestamp": 1597410896, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 249831, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 47576, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 很多高层信这些的，只是不公开表现出来。比如你可以看看周永康的“国师”以及他的祖坟等事。", "timestamp": 1597411470, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 249859, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 47576, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不要干这种事情！", "timestamp": 1597411896, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 249911, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 47576, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 我也觉得，就只是很正常引用中国常用的俗语而已。没必要上纲上线的。", "timestamp": 1597413106, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 249982, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 47576, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "头上三尺有神明这句话难道还是迷信了？", "timestamp": 1597414643, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 249988, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 47576, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 看视频的前后文，“要应验的”", "timestamp": 1597414749, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 250004, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 47576, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 要应验说的是拉清单那个吧。而且这种应该都算是谚语了吧，就是用它的意思而已。这个说迷信还是有点牵强了，你前面说的祖坟啥的如果确实存在是迷信的一种。", "timestamp": 1597415270, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 584, "w": 830}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 47576, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "我害怕了\n尊重zsj教诲", "timestamp": 1597409190, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1606782604, "url": "vk/vkngvfj222zjgv4hgt2r5jcz4pugrayg.jpeg", "vote":